    {
      "id": 20940,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "During login on the login page, login is attempted through the FCTX token. In addition, the login page was implemented through g-recaptcha-response captcha, but an attacker can bypass g-recaptcha-response captcha without FCTX tokens, and login CSRF is possible.\n\nThe issue was fixed by enabling the missing anti-CSRF token validation.",
